data.description: Beautiful 4/2.5 cul-de-sac home, with privacy & tranquility in the middle of town.  Updated, open and bright floor plan with plantation shutters, high ceilings, skylight, gas fireplace/ cooking, gorgeous kitchen with slate backsplash/  granite countertops.  Large master on main floor, large bedrooms up. Park-like, outdoor area with  above ground pool, potting shed/ greenhouse. Exemplary schools.  Minutes to Gruene, Schlitterbahn,Comal & DT NB. Walk to Guadalupe River.
data.whatILove: The location is superb, very peaceful and tranquil but in the center of town, 5 minutes to Greune, Schlitterbaun , downtown New Branufels and the Comal River. The floorplan is light, bright and open with many updates, high ceilings and plantation shutters.  The mature landscaping is gorgeous and there is an above ground pool, potting shed and greenhouse. Exemplary schools!
